==== 主动攻击 ====
{{See also|大炮 (中國網路審查)|旁觀者攻擊}}
[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]]从2015年3月开始，使用一种被称为“大炮”的[[網路戰|網路攻擊]]攻击方案，对可能涉及违反审查要求的特定网站，进行[[分散式阻斷服務攻擊|分散式阻斷服務攻擊]]（DDoS）。<ref name="NYT-China-Said-to-Use-Powerful-New-Weapon-Censor-Internet">{{Cite web |title=China Is Said to Use Powerful New Weapon to Censor Internet |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/11/technology/china-is-said-to-use-powerful-new-weapon-to-censor-internet.html |accessdate=2015-04-11 |author=Perlroth, Nicole |date=2015-04-10 |work=The New York Times |publisher=The New York Times Company |language=en |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150411005836/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/11/technology/china-is-said-to-use-powerful-new-weapon-to-censor-internet.html |archive-date=2015-04-11 }}</ref><ref name="BBC中文網">{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/china/2015/04/150410_china_internet_attack |title=中國採取新方式 網絡封鎖擴大到境外 |author=路西 |date=2015-04-11 |publisher=BBC中文網 |accessdate=2015-04-11 |language=zh-hant |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150414043027/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/trad/china/2015/04/150410_china_internet_attack |archive-date=2015-04-14 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/15/4/10/n4408970.htm |title=中共祭出新武器審查網絡 訪問陸網或被監控 |author=秦雨霏 |date=2015-04-10 |work=大紀元 |accessdate=2015-04-11 |language=zh-tw |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150411094919/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/15/4/10/n4408970.htm |archive-date=2015-04-11 }}</ref>

其中2015年3月针对[[GreatFire|GreatFire]]的攻击，通过包括劫持常见的网站工具脚本植入攻击代码、一些常见浏览器漏洞等方法，攻击其运营在[[内容分发网络|内容分发网络]]的被屏蔽网站的[[镜像站点|镜像站点]]，之后又持续五天对托管其反审查项目的[[GitHub|GitHub]]网站进行攻击，导致网站全球访问速度缓慢。<ref>{{Cite web |title=GitHub System Status |url=https://status.github.com/messages/2015-03-28 |author=GitHub |dead-url=yes |access-date=2016-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170219163334/https://status.github.com/messages/2015-03-28 |archive-date=2017-02-19 }}</ref>中国政府否认有关指责。<ref name="iThome.com.tw">{{Cite web |title=GitHub遭遇史上最大規模DDoS攻擊，反中國網路防火牆專案被鎖定 |url=http://www.ithome.com.tw/news/94872 |accessdate=2015-03-30 |author=陳曉莉 |date=2015-03-30 |publisher=台灣iThome |language=zh-tw |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150331102019/http://www.ithome.com.tw/news/94872 |archive-date=2015-03-31 }}</ref>
